import React from "react";
import { Link, Image, View, Text }  from "react";


function Intro() {
  return (
    <section class="SloganHome">
      <Text class="TextoSloganHome">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. In maximus congue eros in varius.</Text>

      <View class="clear"></View>

      <View class="LogoSolderoxPB">
        <Image src="images/logo_solderox_pb.jpg" width="192" height="60" alt="" />
      </View>
      <View class="LinhaSolderoxPB"></View>

      <View class="clear"></View>

      <View class="RedesSociasHome">
        <Link
          href="https://www.facebook.com/Solderox/"
          target="_blank"
          class="BtRedeSocialFacebook"
        ></Link>
        <Link
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/solderox/"
          target="_blank"
          class="BtRedeSocialLinkedin"
        ></Link>
        <Link
          href="https://www.instagram.com/solderox/"
          target="_blank"
          class="BtRedeSocialInstagram"
        ></Link>
      </View>

      <View class="clear"></View>
    </section>
  );
}

export default Intro;
